.TH "nvme_init_set_features_resv_persist" 9 "nvme_init_set_features_resv_persist" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_set_features_resv_persist \- Initialize passthru command for Reservation Persistence
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_set_features_resv_persist
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "__u32 nsid "  ","
.BI "bool sv "  ","
.BI "bool ptpl "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "nsid" 12
Namespace ID
.IP "sv" 12
Save value across power states
.IP "ptpl" 12
Persist Through Power Loss
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Set Features command with
FID value NVME_FEAT_FID_RESV_PERSIST
